# Unit 3: Lesson 01 - The Need for Programming Languages

## Lesson

* Create instructions using only words to construct a specific arrangement of toy blocks.
* Test the clarity of your instructions by exchanging with another member of the class.
* Brainstorm strategies for effectively communicating the steps of an algorithm.

